data.description:
~Two Family Home: 1 Bedroom Ground Floor. 2 Bedroom Second Floor. 
The Two family Home has a excellent location in the neighborhood of Astoria. One Block from Kaufman Studio 
Close to shops, buses, very close to the subway N/W train. 
25x100 Lot First Floor Features a One Bedroom Apartment One bathroom Apartment. Second Floor Features a Two Bedroom One Bathroom apartment. 
The House Features unused FAR. M1-1 Zoning Land gives the opportunity to build a warehouse.
